<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.ITextureBuffer" Title="ITextureBuffer interface" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    ITextureBuffer
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Declaration">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[class ITextureBuffer;]]></Code>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ITextureBuffer</TypeRef> type is a convenience base interface for all texture buffers. For specific
      functionality provided by texture buffers, please refer to the documentation for the specific texture buffer types
      which extend this interface.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
